ğŸ”¹ Overview Matrix
Layer / Purpose                 | Preferred Case(s)
-------------------------------|-------------------------------
WordPress Hooks & Filters      | Snake case
Plugin Settings & Options      | Snake, Dot
Internal Methods & Props       | Camel, Pascal
Semantic Logging Keys          | Snake, Dot
Database Schema                | Snake case
Autoloaders & Namespaces       | Pascal (classes), Snake (files)
Constants & Enums              | Screaming Snake, Pascal
File Naming (by type)          | Snake, Kebab

