8. ğŸ“ File Naming by Purpose
File Type / Purpose     | Convention       | Example                           | Notes
------------------------|------------------|-----------------------------------|---------------------
PHP class files         | Snake case       | plugin_settings_manager.php       | PSR-4 autoloading
JS modules              | Kebab case       | plugin-handler.js                 | Frontend idioms
Config files            | Snake or kebab   | plugin-config.json                | Editor-friendly
Log files               | Snake case       | plugin_handler.log                | Easy to scan
Markdown/docs           | Kebab case       | plugin-naming-guide.md            | GitHub-friendly
